      <data key="d6">1903</data>
      <data key="d7">1903 was the year Marie Curie, Pierre Curie, and Henri Becquerel were jointly awarded the Nobel Prize in Physics for their groundbreaking work on radioactivity.</data>
      <data key="d9">0.044288</data>
      <data key="d10">1.0</data>
